Fast-paced collection of magic tricks from around the world, voiced by Mel Giedroyc. One Direction's Liam Payne is astonished by what happens when he agrees to have his mind read, there is a trick involving multiplying rabbits courtesy of Michael Carbonaro, and Criss Angel attempts the world record for the most people disappearing at the same time. Mobile phones magically appear, money floats, and one single orange seems to produce an amazing amount of juice. Plus a look at how some tricks are actually done
